<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chung Pathien in atung takin,
 Chisep ding leh suon le pakte-
 Nei ding leh pungto zel dingin!
 Nu leh Pa chuh A hun siem tai.

[V2]
 Zie bang mah chun Aw ka Pathien,
 Vantang ma a kicheng te hi;
 Lungthim khata tui bang luong di'n,
 Vangphatna pien malzawl gel uo!

[V3]
 2. Kumsawt in changbang dam u hen,
 Phung tin luoia, bak bang kai di'n;
 Vang hun pien la, panpih gelin,
 Ginna dik leh chitna hun pie'n.

[V4]
 3. Vawn tam chembang chawi uhen la,
 Na deih banga kipie phal di'n;
 Na min chawihawih zel thei dingin,
 A lungsung u-ah Nang chengin.

[V5]
 4. Thepna leh lei dogal lakah,
 Min siel gela kichengte hi;
 Pathien zanggawp samsuihsa chuh,
 Thihna lo chun phel thei puo'n a.</lyrics>
<title>GOD BRING THEM TOGETHER</title>
<hymn_number>440</hymn_number>
</song>